com.alexvasilkov.android.commons.utils

类 NavHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alexvasilkov.android.commons.utils.NavHelper

  • public class NavHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to navigate between activities with animation.

    Sample usage:
    NavHelper.from(activity).forResult(requestCode).animate(NavHelper.FADE).start(MyActivity.class)
